d after action: actions click_element_by_index, wait are not yet executed', extracted_content='Page changed after action: actions click_element_by_index, wait are not yet executed', include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=True), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory=None, extracted_content='Code: (function(){ try { return document.body.innerText; } catch(e) { return \'Error: \'+e.message; } })()\n\nResult: Skip to content\nSkip to footer\nCommunity\nJobs\nCompanies\nSalaries\nFor Employers\nSearch\nSign In\nAbout Us\nNewsroom\nLeadership\nAdvocacy\nAwards\nBlog\nResearch\nGuides\nAbout Us / Press\nMaking worklife better\n\nSo, what is Glassdoor? We’re a thriving community for workplace conversations, driven by a simple mission to make worklife better, together.\n\nBut the way we do it? That’s not so simple.\n\nEvery day, we’re inspired to build a healthier, more transparent work community for all. Through the products we make and the communities we create, we give people an inside look at companies and careers, so they can find the right job and workplace for them. Together, we’re fostering a world where people have the support and resources they need to make the most of their worklife.\n\nGlassdoor is now a part of Indeed, the #1 job site in the world1 and a global leader in job matching and hiring.\n\nWhat we do\n\nWherever you are on your career journey, Glassdoor makes it easier for workers and companies to find the perfect match.\n\nFor job seekers\n\nWe simplify your search, so you can apply for jobs with confidence. Filter millions of jobs and ratings, talk to professionals, and get smart on salary—then apply with ease.\n\nJoin Glassdoor\nFor employees\n\nWe amplify your voice, so you can enhance your workplace experience. Leave reviews, search and post salaries, and join candid conversations about life at work.\n\nJoin Glassdoor\nFor employers\n\nWe give you a place to shape and share your story, so you can find and keep the best talent. Post jobs, respond to reviews, and gain insights to shape your messaging.\n\nCreate Company Profile\nWork at Glassdoor\n\nWe’re always looking for good people. Innovative people. Folks with grit who embrace transparency, and believe a job should love you back. If you want to get in on a 100% remote company that’s transforming the workplace and redefining what community can do, we should talk!\n\nExplore careers at Glassdoor\nNews you can use\n\nWorkplace trends come and go. When they do, Glassdoor is poised to lead the discussion, offering thought leadership, insights, and advice to help you make sense of it all.\n\nFrom the newsroom\n\nCheck out our latest press releases and media appearances, or search our archive.\n\nRead More\nFrom the blog\n\nWhether you’re interviewing, asking for a raise, or making a big career move, our blog has the tips and tricks you need to shine.\n\nRead More\nFrom our research\n\nGet the latest insights on today’s labor market from Glassdoor’s leading economists and data scientists.\n\nRead More\n\n\xa0\n\n1. Comscore, Total Visits, March 2024\n\nGlassdoor\nAbout / Press\nAwards\nBlog\nResearch\nContact Us\nGuides\nEmployers\nGet a Free Employer Account\nEmployer Center\nInformation\nHelp\nGuidelines\nTerms of Use\nPrivacy & Ad Choices\nDo Not Sell Or Share My Information\nCookie Consent Tool\nSecurity\nWork With Us\nAdvertisers\nCareers\nDownload the App\nandroid icon, opens in new window\napple icon, opens in new window\nglassdoor icon\nfacebook icon, opens in new window\ntwitter icon, opens in new window\nyoutube icon, opens in new window\ninstagram icon, opens in new window\ntiktok icon, opens in new window\nBrowse by:\nCompanies\nJobs\nLocations\nCommunities\nRecent Posts\n\nCopyright © 2008-2025. Glassdoor LLC. "Glassdoor," "Worklife Pro," "Bowls," and logo are proprietary trademarks of Glassdoor LLC.', include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory="Input 'Glassdoor CEO' into element 122.", extracted_content="Input 'Glassdoor CEO' into element 122.", include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory='Sent keys: Enter', extracted_content='Sent keys: Enter', include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory='Waited for 3 seconds', extracted_content='Waited for 3 seconds', include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory='<url>\nhttps://www.glassdoor.com/about/\n</url>\n<query>\nWhat is the name of the CEO of Glassdoor? Provide only the name.\n</query>\n<result>\nInformation not available in the provided page.\n</result>', extracted_content='<url>\nhttps://www.glassdoor.com/about/\n</url>\n<query>\nWhat is the name of the CEO of Glassdoor? Provide only the name.\n</query>\n<result>\nInformation not available in the provided page.\n</result>', include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory=None, extracted_content="Code: (function(){ try { const bodyText = document.body.innerText; const lines = bodyText.split('\\n'); for (let line of lines) { if (/CEO/i.test(line)) { return line.trim(); } } return 'CEO not found'; } catch(e) { return 'Error: '+e.message; } })()\n\nResult: CEO not found", include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=True, success=False, error=None, attachments=[], long_term_memory="Task completed: False - I was unable to locate the CEO name in G